file.name: single_record.yaml
file.content:
openapi: 3.0.1
info:
  title: '''limit'
  version: 0.1.0
servers:
  - url: "{server}:{port}/"
    variables:
      server:
        default: http://localhost
      port:
        default: "9090"
paths:
  /:
    get:
      operationId: operation_get
      responses:
        "200":
          description: Ok
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/Test'
components:
  schemas:
    Test:
      type: object
      properties:
        id:
          type: string
        name:
          type: string
